{"tid":501065,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"盤點Angelababy不濟之作","createTime":"2017-12-16T12:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T06:24:55.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c4ddee4db83265d35c347ccb1a88cba496b8d2a","tid":501065,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"Angelababy嫁給內地男星黃曉明後產下一子，產後迅速開工的Baby接拍首套時裝劇集《創業時代》後，最近確定11月入組拍攝《慾望之城》。不過，憑住超高人氣片約不斷的Baby演技一直備受詬病，日前電視台宣佈《慾望之城》女主角由唐嫣變成Baby出任後，男主角陳道明辭演由吳秀波頂上，隨後又傳出吳秀波辭演的消息，只因大家都唔想同Baby合作。雖然馬上有人跳出來澄清，指吳秀波專誠為戲到米蘭添置服飾，但大部分網友竟然留言讚好，支持吳秀波辭演《慾望之城》。<br />\n<br />\nBaby主演的劇集大部分口碑都差強人意，作為Angelababy的首部古裝電視劇《雲中歌》，Baby在劇中咧嘴、瞪眼、高低眉的表情及拙劣演技讓網友們尬尷不已。劇集《孤芳不自賞》播出後，觀眾對於她的演技也是一直都頗有微詞。即使王家衛監製的電影《擺渡人》，觀察普遍指Baby演技比同劇的梁朝偉、金城武甚至熊黛林都差距甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n也曾有網友爆料稱，Baby在電影《建國大業》時飾演小鳳仙與劉德華飾演的蔡鍔飈戲，在一場離別戲中Baby不管怎樣也流不出眼淚，急得劉德華和導演只能將眼藥水滴入Baby眼中後開始拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/204520_5d6384b0059fc1435ce29305a8328c9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F204520_5d6384b0059fc1435ce29305a8328c9f.jpg&h=66242edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/204521_b25eb63f0dda64102aff4408022474db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F204521_b25eb63f0dda64102aff4408022474db.jpg&h=9b873fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/204521_6fbc9098fe9852190ba0700ecedf8ccd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F204521_6fbc9098fe9852190ba0700ecedf8ccd.jpg&h=933cbfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/204521_c6386e5f5101a265dfd173daf65e374d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F204521_c6386e5f5101a265dfd173daf65e374d.jpg&h=baaa7744&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8174f56ad053ae160d3dfde08d85ac03fa2dccfb","tid":501065,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"麻辣派"},{"pid":"1c30f974f58c711581eacc234882c0260b230de0","tid":501065,"uid":19676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"個樣整出黎既你想佢有咩演技？"},{"pid":"e538c1724b0dd86e7fdc3cb29314ddafb430df6b","tid":501065,"uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"佢無一套代表作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0558d3855daa2dd2a7697b9cddde22aa5a095f3d","tid":501065,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"都唔個佢靠咩紅？<br />\n <br />\n樣又唔係真係咁天姿國色"},{"pid":"374d0929c5b26cfe76fedc358835a0b775e81107","tid":501065,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:57:00.000Z","msg":"all"},{"pid":"883fb460231e8f218661f216b95c9fe978105053","tid":501065,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"JM代表作係咪寒戰/赤道?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ea422eec22ed39302149b9a99dc14ea2b7e98a","tid":501065,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>JM代表作係咪寒戰/赤道?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPromise 唔好再飲"},{"pid":"ca91071421c24382ba49f37e017613555c464363","tid":501065,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"仲有&lt;兇手&gt;俾林家棟打個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2ece3008d0ebfa59e5210c90f40ceb38120a74","tid":501065,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"做model 綜藝都夠啦 拍戲無天份何必勉強"},{"pid":"9a